.org/images/raw/ARG_W.151.271R_OpnObv_UK.jpg"},{"ObjectID":2223,"Title":"Qur'an","Artist":"Iranian","Date":"1151 AH/AD 1738","Medium":"ink and pigments on laid, non-European covered with lacquer","CreditLine":"Walters Art Museum, 1931, by bequest.","URL":"https://purl.thewalters.org/art/W.573","ImageURL":"https://art.thewalters.org/images/raw/PS1_W.573.binding_Fnt_DD_T10_upperboardoutside.jpg"},{"ObjectID":9743,"Title":"Furniture Knob with Name of King","Artist":"Egyptian","Date":"ca. 1340 BC (New Kingdom)","Medium":"Egyptian faience","CreditLine":"Walters Art Museum, 1931, by bequest.","URL":"https://purl.thewalters.org/art/48.404","ImageURL":"https://art.thewalters.org/images/raw/PL2_48.404_Fnt_BW_T98.jpg"},{"ObjectID":1095,"Title":"Nihon hana zue","Artist":"Sasaki Toyokichi (Japanese, active 1855 - 1898); Ogata Gekko (Japanese, 1859 - 1920)","Date":"1892 (Meiji)","Medium":"mulberry paper, pigments","CreditLine":"given to the Walters Art Museum, 1987.","URL":"https://purl.thewalters.org/art/95.202","ImageURL":"https://art.thewalters.org/images/raw/PS3_95.202_Fnt_DD_JP09.jpg"},{"ObjectID":2035,"Title":"Madonna and Child","Artist":"Flemish","Date":"15th century (Renaissance)","Medium":"brass","CreditLine":"The Walters Art Museum","URL":"https://purl.thewalters.org/art/53.36","ImageURL":"https://art.thewalters.org/images/raw/PL2_53.36_Fnt_BW_2005.jpg"},{"ObjectID":4479,"Title":"Emperor on horseback slaying a demon","Artist":"Byzantine","Date":"5th century","Medium":"jasper","CreditLine":"Segredakis","URL":"https://purl.thewalters.org/art/42.1413","ImageURL":"https://art.thewalters.org/images/raw/PL7_42.1413_Fnt_BW_H45.jpg"},{"ObjectID":6171,"Title":"A King Writing His Will (?)","Artist":"American","Date":"","Medium":"Pencil on paper","CreditLine":"The Walters Art Museum","URL":"https://purl.thewalters.org/art/37.1549","ImageURL":"https://art.thewalters.org/images/raw/PL2_37.1549_Fnt_BW_C79.jpg"},{"ObjectID":6359,"Title":"Annunciation and three groups of saints","Arti